## Algorithm Attribution

The NeuroCluster Streamer algorithm is based on research by Michael Katsaros (2025):
"NeuroCluster Streamer: A High-Performance Adaptive Clustering Algorithm for Real-Time Data Streams"

The algorithm implementation is provided under the MIT License with proper attribution
maintained in the source code comments.